# Change policy

## Done means
- [ ] Domain has no imports from driving/driven/nest/drizzle/aws.
- [ ] New IO behind ports; adapters implement and are wired in modules.
- [ ] `pnpm check` passes (types, eslint, prettier).
- [ ] `pnpm test` passes.
- [ ] Event payloads backward-compatible or versioned.
- [ ] SQS handlers retry-safe; no PII in logs.

## Before merge
- Run `verify-changes` skill or manual checklist above.
